Title: Fujitsu REV UTZBD025C Evr Heat Exchanger Unit
Description: Using the exhausted energy from room cooling or heating processes, the Fujitsu REV UTZBD025C energy recovery ventilation heat exchanger provides a comfortable environment with impressive levels of efficiency. Keeping airflow in contact with the unit's element for longer, the REV employs a counter-flow element for better heat exchange when compared to a traditional cross-flow element. Slimline and compact, with a reverse mountable air supply system, this energy recovery ventilation unit offers easy installation in any setting.

Title: Daikin VAM-J VAM1500J Heat Exchanger
Description: Fully ErP compliant, this Daikin VAM-J heat recovery ventilation system recovers waste energy from internal spaces to help reduce the load on your air conditioning or heating system. Designed to deliver fresh air into occupied spaces, this highly efficienct system can reduce the load on heating and cooling systems by up to 73% and can be used in most commercial applications with fresh air requirements up to 2000M³/h. The VAM-J range uses DC fan motors and incorporates specially developed heat exchange elements with no requirement for condensate drainage.
